data.description: 4 Bedroom Colonial in very desirable area of Rehoboth. Features include new granite in kitchen, a newer furnace, hot water tank, 3 season room, laundry on 1st, lawn sprinklers, burglar alarm, walk up attic, generator hookup and mostly finished walk out basement. (Possible additional bedrooms) Located on a quaint, family oriented, hidden cul-de-sac off Brook St. 15 minutes to Providence or Fall River.
